HEADWORD: Ungovernable
<hw>Un*gov"ern*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
governable; not capable of being governed, ruled, or restrained;
licentious; wild; unbridled; <as>as, <ex>ungovernable</ex>
passions</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Un*gov"ern*a*bly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms> <rj><au>Goldsmith.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

